description: The organisation's response to a consultation by the Office for Students (OfS) said that 'universities would be expected to take steps to restrict' unlawful speech.
title: British universities plunged into free speech row after Russell Group issues statement likening gender critics to anti-Semitism

description: Net migration - the number of people moving to Britain minus those leaving - dropped from a record 764,000 in 2022 to 685,000, data from the Office for National Statistics (ONS) showed.
title: Legal net migration fell by 10 per cent last year but it's still at 685,000 - as graphic shows which countries the most arrivals came from
